3. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper deals with fashion items and their compatibility, which can be considered as a form of multimedia analysis. 
4. cs.IR (Information Retrieval): The paper involves learning the compatibility between fashion items, which can be seen as a form of information retrieval.
